{"tid":1047292,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"教育署長大人，可唔可以入嚟傾兩句？","createTime":"2019-03-05T00:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T01:40:47.000Z","uid":188201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fac4aa9d7d86e52310ad72ea61d6bd21cc4e24d1","tid":1047292,"uid":188201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:34:41.000Z","msg":"一個老師同一時間教200人其實係唔係犯法？<br />\n元朗上 live 兩層樓幾間房坐200人每間班房有一個傀儡唔係教書嘅老師，而真正教書嘅應該只有一個老師，咁樣走法律罅嘅話一個人同時教200人我記得好似係犯法，我諗住去申訴專員公署問吓教育署有冇造漏野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖片來自 billy ng Instagram <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/083254_bfa29f1d4a66cc2a9425b5d9d6af6e85.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F083254_bfa29f1d4a66cc2a9425b5d9d6af6e85.png&h=15e4c8cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"908e9fcb7a7518d098c3bb42a028d4bc3b1185a5","tid":1047292,"uid":53122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:38:25.000Z","msg":"無教育署n年"},{"pid":"35efff5003de6e281c4532a310230f59527b4c13","tid":1047292,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:48:26.000Z","msg":"要有助教"},{"pid":"d3f3f68a2efbce1e96f3b7838fd659850872dfe7","tid":1047292,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:22:09.000Z","msg":"教育司署"},{"pid":"8ffa13adedce7a2ee0e9fbefdda47dec4fe13c9d","tid":1047292,"uid":188201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"35efff5003de6e281c4532a310230f59527b4c13","tid":1047292,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:48:26.000Z","msg":"要有助教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:40:47.000Z","msg":"你哋中學去補習冇見過走鬼咩？<br />\n教處一嚟到玻璃房即刻落閘<br />\n跟住助教派野比學生做<br />\n即使比例細過 1:45 <br />\n個補習天王即刻唔夠膽教書<br />\n如果冇犯法點解要走鬼？<br />\n開頭我都唔明白<br />\n我有哥哥嘅朋友做訓導主任同我講<br />\n一個老師教多過45人就一定係犯法<br />\n校處一嚟到就即刻要走鬼"}]}